snippet.title: Maritime Calling Full release Trailer
snippet.description:
Maritime Calling is a narrative-driven RPG in which you lead a daring expedition into the New World. Survive the life at sea, assign sailors to various jobs, fight naval battles, lead island expeditions and break the Empire's hold over the New World in an enchanting seafaring adventure.

Release is coming in April 2022!
